== 早期生活 ==
米歇爾出身於[[紐約市|紐約市]][[布朗克斯|布朗克斯]]的一個猶太家庭，她的母親是一名護士，而她的父親是餐廳老闆。<ref name="TVG">{{cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/lea-michele/bio/252097|title=Lea Michele: Biography|work=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]|accessdate=2010-12-10|archive-date=2010-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101129142022/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/lea-michele/bio/252097|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她是家中的獨女。米歇爾的父親是西班牙系猶太人，但米歇爾信仰天主教，而她的父親亦樂意與米歇爾和她的母親出席教會。<ref name=tcea>Stated on ''[[Inside_the_Actors_Studio|Inside the Actors Studio]]'', 2012. Starting at the 9:40 mark http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xyfCHFy8r-k {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xyfCHFy8r-k |date=20130811073456 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.jvibe.com/Pop_culture/Glee.php "Glee Club Glory"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jvibe.com/Pop_culture/Glee.php |date=20101216232545 }} Jvibe.com</ref> 。

雖然米歇爾出身於[[紐約市|紐約市]]，但她是在[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]長大的<ref>[http://www.radaronline.com/exclusives/2010/05/exclusive-glee-star-lea-micheles-childhood-photos "EXCLUSIVE: Glee Star Lea Michele's Childhood Photos"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.radaronline.com/exclusives/2010/05/exclusive-glee-star-lea-micheles-childhood-photos |date=20131221200439 }} May 21, 2010, Radar Online</ref>，她亦曾有一年在[[多倫多|多倫多]]生活，後來她在[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]修讀藝術。

== 職業生涯 == 

=== [[百老匯|百老匯]]生涯 ===
早在1995年，米歇爾已開始她的百老匯首演，飾演《[[孤星淚|孤星淚]]》的幼年珂賽特（Cosette）。<ref>Waterman, Lauren.[http://www.teenvogue.com/industry/blogs/entertainment/2009/10/lea-michele.html "High School Musical: Glee's Lea Michele"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.teenvogue.com/industry/blogs/entertainment/2009/10/lea-michele.html |date=20120129134241 }} teenvogue.com, October 12, 2009</ref>在2004年米歇爾出演了百老匯音樂劇《[[:en:Fiddler_on_the_Roof|屋上提琴手]]》。<ref>Jones, Kenneth.[http://www.playbill.com/news/article/84589-Not-Your-Zaydes-Fiddler-on-the-Roof-Leveauxs-Fresh-Revival-Opens-on-Broadway-Feb-26 "Not Your Zayde's 'Fiddler on the Roof': Leveaux's Fresh Revival Opens on Broadway Feb. 26"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/84589-Not-Your-Zaydes-Fiddler-on-the-Roof-Leveauxs-Fresh-Revival-Opens-on-Broadway-Feb-26 |date=20130523203724 }} playbill.com, February 26, 2004</ref>

米歇爾在2006年在《[[:en:Spring_Awakening|春醒]]》中飾演Wendla。<ref name="ddesk">{{cite web |url=http://www.dramadesk.com/ |title=Drama Desk Official website |publisher=Dramadesk.com |date= |accessdate=2012-02-13 |archive-date=2012-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212174706/http://dramadesk.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在同年，《[[孤星淚|孤星淚]]》再次被搬上[[百老匯|百老匯]]的舞台，米歇爾被邀請飾演愛潘妮（Éponine）<ref>[http://www.playbill.com/celebritybuzz/article/120298.html-DIVA-TALK-Chatting-with-Spring-Awakening-Les-Mizs-Lea-Michele-Plus-News-of-Ebersole-Eder "Diva Talk: Chatting With 'Spring Awakening'/'Les-Mizs' Lea Michele Plus News of Ebersole Eder"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120909213708/http://www.playbill.com/celebritybuzz/article/120298.html-DIVA-TALK-Chatting-with-Spring-Awakening-Les-Mizs-Lea-Michele-Plus-News-of-Ebersole-Eder |date=2012-09-09 }} playbill.com</ref>，但米歇爾選擇繼續出演《[[:en:Spring_Awakening|春醒]]》，她因此劇被Drama Desk Awards提名為音樂類別傑出女演員。<ref name="rooney"/>D. Rooney.[https://archive.is/20130105132944/www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=awardcentral&jump=features&id=tonypreview&articleid=VR1117963881 "Musicals pose Tony voting crunch"], ''Variety.com'', April 26, 2007</

=== 《[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]》 ===
米歇爾在[[FOX|FOX]]的電視劇《[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]》（Glee）中飾演[[:en:Rachel_Berry|瑞秋·貝瑞]](Rachel Berry)，是劇中的女主角和主唱。在開拍歡樂合唱團前，製作人[[萊恩·墨菲_(編劇)|萊恩·墨菲]]匆忙地尋找合適的演員，萊恩在[[百老匯|百老匯]]花了三個月時間，最終在那裡他發現了米歇爾。<ref name="rewrite">{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-ca-gleestage26-2009apr26,0,1653470.story |title=Video: 'Glee' team rewrites the school musical |first=Denise |last=Martin |publisher=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=April 26, 2009 |accessdate=May 19, 2009 |archive-date=2013-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026203256/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-ca-gleestage26-2009apr26,0,1653470.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[:en:Rachel_Berry|瑞秋·貝瑞]]一角是專門為米歇爾度身訂做。<ref name="bs">{{cite web|url=http://www.backstage.com/bso/news-and-features-features/life-stages-1004009175.story|title=Life Stages|last=Kuhn|first=Sarah|date=September 3, 2009|work=[[Back_Stage|Back Stage]]|accessdate=September 5, 2009|archive-date=2009-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090905231849/http://www.backstage.com/bso/news-and-features-features/life-stages-1004009175.story|dead-url=no}}</ref> 米歇爾決定飾演瑞秋一角是因為她認為「瑞秋」不只是一個歌手，她對藝術亦充滿熱誠，[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]亦在電視上傳播「藝術的重要」及「忠於自己」的信息。<ref name="NYPost">{{cite web|url=http://blogs.nypost.com/popwrap/archives/2009/05/glee_cast_interview.html|title=Meet The Cast of 'Glee,' I Did!|last=Wieselman|first=Jarett|date=May 19, 2009|work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|accessdate=June 1, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090525103629/http://blogs.nypost.com/popwrap/archives/2009/05/glee_cast_interview.html|archivedate=2009-05-25}}</ref>

米歇爾在《歡樂合唱團》中的唱歌與演技都廣受好評，更憑此劇贏得了眾多獎項，米歇爾曾被[[格林美獎|格林美獎]]、[[金球獎|金球獎]]、[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]等提名，她更憑此劇分別連續三屆和兩屆在[[青少年票選獎|青少年票選獎]]和[[全美民選獎|全美民選獎]]獲得喜劇女演員獎項。米歇爾在2010年同在《[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]》演出的[[克里斯·柯爾弗|克里斯·柯爾弗]]入選為2011年時代百大人物。米歇爾在[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]所有女演員之中她擁有最多獨唱歌曲，包辦了超過一半以上以的獨唱及合唱歌曲。米歇爾在[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]第一季中翻唱[[:en:The_All-American_Rejects|The All-American Rejects]] 的"Gives You Hell"在[[Billboard_Hot_100|Billboard Hot 100]]排行前40名<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a216180/glee-cover-takes-top-spot-in-ireland.html|title= Music - News - 'Glee' cover takes top spot in Ireland - Digital Spy|author= Daniel Kilkelley|publisher= DigitalSpy.com|date= April 29, 2010|accessdate= 2013-08-28|archive-date= 2011-07-10|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110710125535/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a216180/glee-cover-takes-top-spot-in-ireland.html|dead-url= no}}<!-- Bot generated title --></ref>，在[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]20首最暢銷歌曲中米歇爾佔了超過一半<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/150414/whats-up-lea-michele-all-about-glee-newfound-fame-and-sigh-jonathan-groff|title=What's Up, Lea Michele? All About Glee, Newfound Fame and (Sigh!) Jonathan Groff|date=April 13, 2010|author=Kathy Henderson|publisher=Broadway.com|accessdate=May 17, 2011|archive-date=2011-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102173023/http://www.broadway.com/buzz/150414/whats-up-lea-michele-all-about-glee-newfound-fame-and-sigh-jonathan-groff/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。米歇爾在2011年首次被[[格林美獎|格林美獎]]提名，第一項是最佳流行樂隊/組合(Don't Stop Believin')，第二項是最佳影視媒體作品作曲專輯 ([[歡樂合唱團第一輯|歡樂合唱團第一輯]])<ref name= MTV2>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1653441/glee-star-lea-michele-celebrates-grammy-nominations.jhtml|title='Glee' Star Lea Michele Celebrates Two Grammy Nominations|date=December 2, 2010|work=Jocelyn Vena|publisher=MTV|accessdate=February 15, 2011|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629151051/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1653441/glee-star-lea-michele-celebrates-grammy-nominations.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，米歇爾對她首次被[[格林美獎|格林美獎]]提名十分興奮，「"Don't Stop Believin'"被提名我感到很高興，因為這是給[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]所有演員的，讓大家繼續努力」。<ref name= globes>{{cite news|url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/blog/2010/12/the-68th-annual-golden-globe-awards-nominations/|title=The 68th Annual Golden Globe Awards Nominations|date=December 14, 2011|publisher=[[Golden_Globes|Golden Globes]]|accessdate=February 15, 2011|archive-date=2011-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110103061520/http://www.goldenglobes.org/blog/2010/12/the-68th-annual-golden-globe-awards-nominations/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在2010年，[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]在美國舉辦了巡迴演唱會 — [[:en:Glee_Live!_In_Concert!|歡樂合唱團演唱會]]，到過[[鳳凰城|鳳凰城]]、[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]、[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]、[[紐約|紐約]]等，米歇爾及劇中演員都在演唱會中繼續飾演劇中角色。

=== 個人專輯《[[:en:Louder_(album)|Louder]]》及其他工作 ===
在2011年，米歇爾首次拍攝電影，與多位巨星合作電影《[[101次新年快樂|101次新年快樂]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/NEFflSc4xeE2IH|title=Glee's Lea Michele to Celebrate New Year's Eve|publisher=MovieWeb.com|date=October 22, 2010|accessdate=2010-11-20|archive-date=2010-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028121712/http://www.movieweb.com/news/NEFflSc4xeE2IH|dead-url=no}}</ref>。米歇爾亦在2014年上映的《[[:en:Dorothy_of_Oz_(film)|奧茲國的桃樂絲]]》為主角Dorothy配音。2012年9月，米歇爾宣佈她正在準備第一張個人專輯，她表示錄製過程相當緩慢。米歇爾希望她的專輯更有流行和搖滾的風格，不會因她是百老匯演員而受百老匯風格影響。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a409237/glee-star-lea-michele-working-on-debut-album.html|title=Lea begins work on debut solo album|date=October 2, 2012|accessdate=October 2, 2012|archive-date=2012-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121117024336/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a409237/glee-star-lea-michele-working-on-debut-album.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

